name: ShadowGoblin
body:
### Welcome to ShadowGoblin (Cutting Edge).
This is where you can get the cutting edge version of ShadowGoblin.

### Installation
1. Download and extract the .zip
2. Rename extracted folder to `Probably`,
3. Place folder in your `World of Warcraft/Interface/Addons` folder.

### Contribution 
1. Create a fork.
2. Make changes and improve PE.
3. Create a pull request.
